<p>The alignment factor, as a normalized value between 0.0 and 1.0</p><p>The factor depends on the <link xref="Clutter.AlignConstraint-align-axis">Clutter.AlignConstraint:align-axis</link> property:
with an align-axis value of %CLUTTER_ALIGN_X_AXIS, 0.0 means left and
1.0 means right; with a value of %CLUTTER_ALIGN_Y_AXIS, 0.0 means top
and 1.0 means bottom.</p>
